From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Patric Stout <github@truebrain.nl>
Date: Fri, 3 Jul 2026 21:35:54 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 09/13] fix: missing incref with GetThreadScheduleManager()

References from GetThreadScheduleManager should be increased before
returned. Other places do this correctly, but in this function it
was missed.
---
 src/SchedulerModule.cpp | 4 +++-
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/src/SchedulerModule.cpp b/src/SchedulerModule.cpp
index 6e4a28f..ca1d499 100644
--- a/src/SchedulerModule.cpp
+++ b/src/SchedulerModule.cpp
@@ -792,7 +792,9 @@ extern "C"
 	static PyObject* PyScheduler_GetScheduler( )
 	{
 		GILRAII gil;
-		return ScheduleManager::GetThreadScheduleManager()->PythonObject();
+		ScheduleManager* scheduleManager = ScheduleManager::GetThreadScheduleManager();
+		scheduleManager->Incref();
+		return scheduleManager->PythonObject();
 	}
 
     /// @brief Yield execution of current tasklet. Tasklet is added to end of run queue
